owlSpeak.engine.his

Class Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • owlSpeak.engine.his.Field

  • public class Field
extends java.lang.Object
    The Field class represents a field (or slot) which can be addressed during the dialogue, e.g., in a flight booking dialogue it may be "origin" or "destination".
    Version:
    0.1
    Author:
    Stefan Ultes <stefan.ultes@uni-ulm.de>
